WITH SupplierStats AS (
    SELECT 
        s.s_suppkey,
        s.s_name,
        s.s_nationkey,
        SUM(ps.ps_availqty) AS total_available_quantity,
        COUNT(DISTINCT ps.ps_partkey) AS distinct_parts_supplied,
        STRING_AGG(DISTINCT p.p_name, ', ') AS part_names
    FROM supplier s
    JOIN partsupp ps ON s.s_suppkey = ps.ps_suppkey
    JOIN part p ON ps.ps_partkey = p.p_partkey
    GROUP BY s.s_suppkey, s.s_name, s.s_nationkey
),
NationRegions AS (
    SELECT 
        n.n_nationkey,
        n.n_name,
        r.r_regionkey,
        r.r_name AS region_name
    FROM nation n
    JOIN region r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey
)
SELECT 
    nw.n_name AS nation_name,
    nr.region_name,
    ss.s_name AS supplier_name,
    ss.total_available_quantity,
    ss.distinct_parts_supplied,
    ss.part_names,
    cast('1998-10-01' as date) AS benchmark_date
FROM SupplierStats ss
JOIN NationRegions nr ON ss.s_nationkey = nr.n_nationkey
JOIN nation nw ON nr.n_nationkey = nw.n_nationkey
WHERE ss.total_available_quantity > 1000
ORDER BY ss.total_available_quantity DESC

INNER JOIN ("part" INNER JOIN "partsupp" ON "part"."p_partkey" = "partsupp"."ps_partkey") ON "supplier"."s_suppkey" = "partsupp"."ps_suppkey"
GROUP BY "supplier"."s_suppkey", "supplier"."s_name", "supplier"."s_nationkey"
HAVING SUM("partsupp"."ps_availqty") > 1000) AS "t3"
INNER JOIN ("s1" INNER JOIN "nation" AS "nation0" ON "s1"."N_NATIONKEY" = "nation0"."n_nationkey") ON "t3"."S_NATIONKEY" = "s1"."N_NATIONKEY"
ORDER BY "t3"."TOTAL_AVAILABLE_QUANTITY" DESC NULLS FIRST) AS "t5"

SELECT COALESCE("r_regionkey", "r_regionkey") AS "r_regionkey", "r_name", "r_comment"
FROM "region"

SELECT COALESCE("t5"."NATION_NAME", "t5"."NATION_NAME") AS "NATION_NAME", "t5"."REGION_NAME", "t5"."SUPPLIER_NAME", "t5"."TOTAL_AVAILABLE_QUANTITY", "t5"."DISTINCT_PARTS_SUPPLIED", "t5"."PART_NAMES", "t5"."BENCHMARK_DATE"
FROM (SELECT "nation0"."n_name" AS "NATION_NAME", "t3"."REGION_NAME", "t2"."S_NAME" AS "SUPPLIER_NAME", "t2"."TOTAL_AVAILABLE_QUANTITY", "t2"."DISTINCT_PARTS_SUPPLIED", "t2"."PART_NAMES", DATE '1998-10-01' AS "BENCHMARK_DATE"
FROM (SELECT "supplier"."s_suppkey" AS "S_SUPPKEY", "supplier"."s_name" AS "S_NAME", "supplier"."s_nationkey" AS "S_NATIONKEY", SUM("partsupp"."ps_availqty") AS "TOTAL_AVAILABLE_QUANTITY", COUNT(DISTINCT "partsupp"."ps_partkey") AS "DISTINCT_PARTS_SUPPLIED", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "part"."p_name", ', ') AS "PART_NAMES"
FROM "supplier"
INNER JOIN ("part" INNER JOIN "partsupp" ON "part"."p_partkey" = "partsupp"."ps_partkey") ON "supplier"."s_suppkey" = "partsupp"."ps_suppkey"
GROUP BY "supplier"."s_suppkey", "supplier"."s_name", "supplier"."s_nationkey"
HAVING SUM("partsupp"."ps_availqty") > 1000) AS "t2"
INNER JOIN ((SELECT "nation"."n_nationkey" AS "N_NATIONKEY", "nation"."n_name" AS "N_NAME", "s1"."r_regionkey" AS "R_REGIONKEY", "s1"."r_name" AS "REGION_NAME"
FROM "s1"
INNER JOIN "nation" ON "s1"."r_regionkey" = "nation"."n_regionkey") AS "t3" INNER JOIN "nation" AS "nation0" ON "t3"."N_NATIONKEY" = "nation0"."n_nationkey") ON "t2"."S_NATIONKEY" = "t3"."N_NATIONKEY"
ORDER BY "t2"."TOTAL_AVAILABLE_QUANTITY" DESC NULLS FIRST) AS "t5"

SELECT COALESCE("n_nationkey", "n_nationkey") AS "n_nationkey", "n_name", "n_regionkey", "n_comment"
FROM "nation"

SELECT COALESCE("t5"."NATION_NAME", "t5"."NATION_NAME") AS "NATION_NAME", "t5"."REGION_NAME", "t5"."SUPPLIER_NAME", "t5"."TOTAL_AVAILABLE_QUANTITY", "t5"."DISTINCT_PARTS_SUPPLIED", "t5"."PART_NAMES", "t5"."BENCHMARK_DATE"
FROM (SELECT "s10"."n_name" AS "NATION_NAME", "t3"."REGION_NAME", "t2"."S_NAME" AS "SUPPLIER_NAME", "t2"."TOTAL_AVAILABLE_QUANTITY", "t2"."DISTINCT_PARTS_SUPPLIED", "t2"."PART_NAMES", DATE '1998-10-01' AS "BENCHMARK_DATE"
FROM (SELECT "supplier"."s_suppkey" AS "S_SUPPKEY", "supplier"."s_name" AS "S_NAME", "supplier"."s_nationkey" AS "S_NATIONKEY", SUM("partsupp"."ps_availqty") AS "TOTAL_AVAILABLE_QUANTITY", COUNT(DISTINCT "partsupp"."ps_partkey") AS "DISTINCT_PARTS_SUPPLIED", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "part"."p_name", ', ') AS "PART_NAMES"
FROM "supplier"
INNER JOIN ("part" INNER JOIN "partsupp" ON "part"."p_partkey" = "partsupp"."ps_partkey") ON "supplier"."s_suppkey" = "partsupp"."ps_suppkey"
GROUP BY "supplier"."s_suppkey", "supplier"."s_name", "supplier"."s_nationkey"
HAVING SUM("partsupp"."ps_availqty") > 1000) AS "t2"
INNER JOIN ((SELECT "s1"."n_nationkey" AS "N_NATIONKEY", "s1"."n_name" AS "N_NAME", "region"."r_regionkey" AS "R_REGIONKEY", "region"."r_name" AS "REGION_NAME"
FROM "region"
INNER JOIN "s1" ON "region"."r_regionkey" = "s1"."n_regionkey") AS "t3" INNER JOIN "s1" AS "s10" ON "t3"."N_NATIONKEY" = "s10"."n_nationkey") ON "t2"."S_NATIONKEY" = "t3"."N_NATIONKEY"
ORDER BY "t2"."TOTAL_AVAILABLE_QUANTITY" DESC NULLS FIRST) AS "t5"
